It doesn't take long for new untreated oak slats to become weathered.  I
left my new white oak bows exposed to the elements so they would weather,
and they looked about 5 years old in a couple of months sun/rain/snow
exposure.

FWIW,

Tom Buese-w/ new weathered oak bows on the DC
